{"tid":2146519,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼反光衣、記者證之後 黑警癲到要記者出示受薪證明 否則用限聚令告9你","createTime":"2020-08-08T15:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T16:51:17.000Z","uid":321059,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7246676ac12fd35e7f79a57947b30618d94415b2","tid":2146519,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"今日（8 日）是科大學生周梓樂去世 9 個月，《立場新聞》一名攝影記者在將軍澳採訪市民悼念行動期間，與另外兩名記者一同被警員截查。《立場》記者當時身穿反光衣，出示記者證和身份證後，仍被警員要求證明是「受薪員工」，最後更指示記者致電同事以證明身份。<br />\n<br />\n兩名同行記者最終被發限聚令告票，警員稱二人不是記者，「你哋行埋一齊呢，違反咗限聚令，淨係告佢哋兩個，因為佢兩個唔係記者，唔喺度做嘢。」《立場》正就警方要求記者工作時出示「受薪證明」一事，向警方查詢準則和根據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3340652879353642/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3340652879353642%2F&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW1MsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=73b272b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3340652879353642/</a>"},{"pid":"9472d240821961df60a10eb334c93764bdb189dc","tid":2146519,"uid":1989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"狗王落左鑊班散仔發狗瘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b19fa624d0e5bd580333755ae2625c8ef21b4f","tid":2146519,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲可以放上 Twitter"},{"pid":"d99bfcdea9f7d4bf5a9cda57167aede2ebbff450","tid":2146519,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"由牠們告，交唔交罰款我主場"},{"pid":"809b3c18a860f8972f97f1021f28e70df55aba06","tid":2146519,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}